# TxMA Deployment Metrics
This dashboard displays deployment metrics for the TxMA team. The aim being to identify any areas of the pipeline that can be optimised.

tiles.name: Markdown
tiles.markdown:
## Secure Pipelines Versions


The metrics in this section are all gathered via Secure Pipelines. They indicate what version of Secure Pipelines each of the pipeline stacks is currently using.

----

tiles.name: Markdown
tiles.markdown:
### Pipeline Versions

Versions of the secure pipelines currently being used for deployments on INT and Prod

tiles.name: Markdown
tiles.markdown:
## Currently deployed applications

The versions of each application deployed to the Prod environments. The commit hash, and deployment time are shown for each application.
